parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of power door locks can lead to safety issues, such as being unable to exit the vehicle in an emergency situation.
symptoms: Doors won't lock or unlock with key fob or switches
doors may stick or not open from inside or outside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Headlight failure can lead to reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: Headlights shut off or fail to turn on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag light and sensor issues can lead to uncertainty about airbag deployment in the event of an accident, potentially causing harm to occupants.
symptoms: passenger airbag turns off even when occupied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failure can lead to various safety issues, including loss of power, reduced visibility, and increased risk of accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Throttle Seal and Engine Reduced Power Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Throttle seal and engine reduced power issues can lead to loss of acceleration, increasing the risk of accidents, especially on highways.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag System Failure (Passenger Presence System Malfunction)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating that the airbags may not deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates intermittently
the airbag light stays on continuously
the airbag light turns on and off while driving
the airbag light comes on when the passenger seat is occupied or unoccupied
the airbag light is accompanied by a seat belt warning light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlamp driver module can cause the headlights to fail, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: the headlights shut off while driving
the headlights do not turn on
the headlights are dim or weak.
